drm/amdkfd: Introduce XGMI SDMA queue type

Existing QUEUE_TYPE_SDMA means PCIe optimized SDMA queues.
Introduce a new QUEUE_TYPE_SDMA_XGMI, which is optimized
for non-PCIe transfer such as XGMI.

